  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "E-commerce Executive",
  "description": "<p>Our company fosters a dynamic and friendly environment where everyone knows each other and work together towards a common goal. We prioritize teamwork, open communication and mutual support. Be part of our team where every voice matters and every contribution counts!</p><p>- Reply to and manage customer enquiries across online platforms</p><p>- Manage and grow e-commerce sales on platforms such as Amazon, Shopee, Lazada, TikTok Shop, etc.</p><p>- Monitor product listings, pricing, promotions, and stock availability</p><p>- Handle customer returns, exchanges, and related follow-ups</p><p>- Plan, join, and execute online campaigns and platform-led promotions</p><p>- Set up and manage online flash deals and special sales events</p><p>- Extract and prepare monthly performance reports for each e-commerce platform</p><p>- Analyze sales data and platform insights to track performance and identify growth opportunities</p><p>- Propose and implement ideas to increase sales and conversion rates</p><p>- Develop strategies to reduce customer enquiries and return rates</p><p>- Plan and execute basic marketing activities, including social media postings</p><p>- Coordinate with internal teams to ensure smooth order fulfillment and customer experience</p><p>- Manage and guide interns to streamline workload and daily operations</p><p>- Ensure processes are systematic, organized, and scalable</p><p>- Take ownership of assigned platforms and deliver results independently</p><p>Working Hours:</p><p>Mon - Fri, 9:00am - 6:00pm</p><p>Sat, 9:00am - 1pm</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Salary: $2,500 - $4,000</strong></p><p>- Variable bonus</p><p>- Commission </p><p>- Birthday Leave<br /><br />- Annual Leave</p><p><br /></p><p>If you are independent and experienced warehouse personnel looking for a new challenge. Please submit your resume to weekiat@packman.sg</p>",
